dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Sauk County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: These data layers represent roads and Right of Ways (ROW) for Sauk County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Sauk_Roads_ROW_2018.gdb'. [This feature class contains detailed line work supporting Sauk Counties road network and contains street name, classification, and address range attributes. The primary division of a simultaneous conveyance and generally referred to as lots, units, or common elements.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://data-saukgis.opendata.arcgis.com.
